#: content/_index.md:15
msgid ""
"<!--\n"
"Show this once the Beta milestone is complete!\n"
"\n"
"Introducing **KDE Linux**, a free and open-source operating system built by KDE that can turbocharge new computers and breathe life into old ones.\n"
"\n"
"KDE Linux is designed for general use, including the best implementation of everything KDE has to offer, with the most advanced technologies.-->\n"
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:22
msgid "**Help KDE build the next big thing!**"
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:24
msgid ""
"**KDE Linux** is a free, open-source, user-focused operating system being "
"built by KDE to include the best implementation of everything KDE has to "
"offer, using the most advanced technologies. Learn more on [the project’s "
"README](https://invent.kde.org/kde-linux/kde-linux#kde-linux)."
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:28
msgid ""
"Designed to be safe, maintainable, functional, and modern, KDE Linux will be"
" the best choice for home use, enterprise workstations, public institutions,"
" pre-installation on computers you can buy, and more."
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:30
msgid ""
"…Eventually! We’re not there yet, and need your help to make this goal a "
"reality."
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:32
msgid ""
"{{< linux/button src=\"docs/install\" description=\"Install KDE Linux\" >}} "
"{{< linux/button src=\"docs/\" description=\"Read the docs\" >}}"
msgstr ""

