#: content/_index.md:216
msgid ""
"A great deal of information on the internet and AI chatbots is wrong, "
"outdated, or doesn’t apply to KDE Linux."
msgstr ""

#: content/_index.md:218
msgid ""
"Before consulting those sources, first look for an answer in [KDE Linux’s "
"documentation](/docs). Common topics include:"
